TITLE:: ReaperServer
summary:: Singleton connection to Reaper OSC Interface
categories:: OSC
related:: Classes/PReaper

DESCRIPTION::
Connecting to an instance of Reaper through OSC. For now, just a wrapper to call play/stop/time from one single instance.


EXAMPLES::

ReaperServer.defaultHost;
ReaperServer.defaultPort;

ReaperServer() === ReaperServer();
ReaperServer().server.host;
ReaperServer().server.port;
